msgid "{0}层迟缓"
msgstr "{0} stacks Slow"

#: ../Datatable/Dist\Skill\Skill.gd:26
msgid ""
"战斗后获得{0}层【迟缓】状态，每层迟缓使得战斗时敌人多攻击二回合\n"
"每{1}点护盾会减少一层实际获得的状态"
msgstr ""
"After combat, gain {0} stacks of Slow. Each stack causes enemies to gain 2 "
"additional attack turns in a combat.\n"
"For every {1} Shield, reduce the actual stacks gained by 1."

#: ../Datatable/Dist\Skill\Skill.gd:27
msgid "{0}层诅咒"
msgstr "{0} stacks Curse"

#: ../Datatable/Dist\Skill\Skill.gd:27
