"When you pass by this enemy's cross-shaped area, it deals {0} damage(can be "
"reduced by shield) and will be pushed back one grid. This pushback cannot "
"pass through other enemies or items."

#: ../Datatable/Dist\Skill\Skill.gd:39
msgid "{0}格领域"
msgstr "{0} tiles Realm"

#: ../Datatable/Dist\Skill\Skill.gd:39
msgid "角色经过该敌人{0}格范围内时受到{1}点伤害，可被护盾减免"
